```mermaid
flowchart TB
    L["lane .md file task blocks"]
    P["poll_lane()"]
    R["Sort pick priority"]
    E["execute(task)"]
    W["write_result()"]
    H["Heartbeat worker.json"]
    P --> R --> E --> W --> P
    L <--> P
    W -.-> H
    H -.-> S["Supervisor restart"]
    W --> T1["Fast Worker 30-60s"]
    W --> T2["Medium Worker 2-5min"]
    W --> T3["Slow Worker 5-15min"]
```
